    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I change a little bit the extendTheme proposal. \n\nWe need both because we want to keep the ability to extend a theme by classNames. But we also want to be able to extend it by inline style.\nIn one case you will pass a map of themeKeys/className (string), and in the other case a map of themeKeys/inlineStyle (object).\n\nIs it clearer ?  \n",
